title: Brenda Jackson-One Winter's Night & Feeling the Heat
description:
Feeling the Heat

Romance

Award-winning author Brenda Jackson is no stranger to the New York Times and USA Today best-seller lists. Feeling the Heat stars rugged Dr. Micah Westmoreland, a man doing his all to regain the trust and love of Kalina Daniels. Their romance broke off because of a perceived betrayal, which Kalina has never forgiven. Now Micah is determined to right this past wrong and be the man Kalina deserves.

One Winter's Night

New York Times and USA Today best-selling author Brenda Jackson has received an RWA Lifetime Achievement Award for her stunning contemporary romances. One Winter's Night delivers the next chapter in the sizzling Westmoreland saga. Falling into bed with Alpha Blake, his company's ravishing new party planner, wasn't Riley Westmoreland's plan -- but now that it's happened, he knows one night will never be enough. So when Alpha's past puts their budding relationship in jeopardy, Riley vows to find a solution, and capture her heart
